section.def:
driver
                (駕駛人), in relation to a vehicle, means any person
            who is in charge of or assisting in the control of the vehicle;

subparagraph.content:
where the permit is in respect of China trade cargo, the time when the
                        vessel that carried the cargo leaves the public cargo working area or public
                        water-front;

for the mobile office or mobile shelter specified in the permit or any
                        mobile office or mobile shelter substituted, respectively, therefor under
                        paragraph (5);
